<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>关于 MindFlow</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
    <style>
        /* === 1. 复用首页的极简背景 === */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #fdfbfb 0%, #ebedee 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #444;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        /* === 2. 玻璃面板通用样式 === */
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            border-radius: 20px; /* 圆角稍微大一点 */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .glass-panel:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        }

        /* === 3. 导航栏样式 (保持一致) === */
        .navbar-custom {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 12px 0;
        }

        /* 品牌渐变字 */
        .brand-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        /* 渐变按钮 */
        .btn-gradient-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-gradient-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #764ba2 0%, #667eea 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.3);
            color: white;
        }

        /* === 4. 特性图标渐变 === */
        .feature-icon-wrapper {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); /* 淡紫色背景 */
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .glass-panel:hover .feature-icon-wrapper {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            transform: rotateY(180deg); /* 趣味旋转效果 */
        }

        /* === 5. 技术栈徽章 === */
        .tech-badge {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            color: #555;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .tech-badge:hover {
            color: #667eea;
            border-color: #667eea;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light navbar-custom sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand brand-gradient d-flex align-items-center gap-2" href="/">
                <i class="bi bi-wind"></i> MindFlow
            </a>
            <div class="ms-auto">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm rounded-pill px-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> 返回首页
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 主体内容 -->
    <div class="container py-5">
        
        <!-- 1. Hero 区域 -->
        <div class="text-center mb-5 pb-3">
            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3 brand-gradient">思维流淌的地方</h1>
            <p class="lead text-secondary mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
                MindFlow 是一个专注于极简写作与深度交流的内容平台。<br>
                我们相信，每一个微小的想法，都值得被记录和分享。
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-gradient-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 shadow-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-github"></i> 访问 GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. 核心特性 (3张玻璃卡片) -->
        <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
            <!-- Markdown -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="glass-panel p-5 text-center h-100">
                    <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="bi bi-markdown"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Markdown 支持</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">原生的 Markdown 渲染引擎，让排版回归纯粹，专注于内容创作本身，支持代码高亮与即时预览。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 实时交互 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="glass-panel p-5 text-center h-100">
                    <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">实时交互</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">基于 Ajax 技术构建的无刷新评论系统，让思想的碰撞更加流畅，拒绝页面的频繁重载。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 权限管理 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="glass-panel p-5 text-center h-100">
                    <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">权限管理</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">完善的 RBAC 角色权限控制体系，为创作者提供安全的内容管理环境，支持管理员高级操作。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. 技术架构 (Under the Hood) -->
        <div class="glass-panel p-5 text-center">
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4">Under the Hood</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">MindFlow 基于现代化的 Web 技术栈构建，追求性能与开发体验的平衡。</p>
            
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-filetype-js"></i> Node.js</span>
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-server"></i> Express</span>
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-database"></i> MongoDB</span>
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-window"></i> EJS SSR</span>
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-bootstrap"></i> Bootstrap 5</span>
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> Ajax / Fetch</span>
                <span class="tech-badge"><i class="bi bi-layout-wtf"></i> MVC 架构</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 底部版权 -->
        <div class="text-center mt-5 text-muted small">
            <p>&copy; 2026 MindFlow Project. Designed by sunrise. <i class="bi bi-heart-fill text-danger"></i></p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>